><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-549bd40 elementor-widget elementor-widget-menu-anchor\" data-id=\"549bd40\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"menu-anchor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-menu-anchor\" id=\"about\"><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-73f495c elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"73f495c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>I am a Robotics Engineering student at Polytech Dijon, currently completing my final internship before graduating with a <em>Dipl\u00f4me d&#8217;Ing\u00e9nieur<\/em> (equivalent to an MSc in Robotics Engineering).&nbsp;During my studies, I completed internships at Bosch Research in Germany and Singapore, as well as at Schneider Electric in France, gaining practical experience in robotics, automation, embedded systems, and product development.<\/p>\n<p>This portfolio brings together a selection of the robotics and 3D printing projects I have worked on throughout my academic and professional journey. While it does not include every project, such as my work in computer vision and AI, it provides an overview of the engineering challenges I have enjoyed tackling and the skills I have developed along the way.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a276b3d e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"a276b3d\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-00d93aa elementor-widget elementor-widget-button\" data-id=\"00d93aa\" data-